> **"Build the Future from the Beginning"**

GENXAIS is a modularized, intelligent development framework that implements the APM (Agile Project Management) methodology through AI-driven multi-agent collaboration. It provides systematic project development from vision to implementation with robust error handling and knowledge management.

## ğŸŒŸ Features

- ğŸ¯ **APM Methodology**: VAN â†’ PLAN â†’ CREATE â†’ IMPLEMENT â†’ REFLECT
- ğŸ¤– **Multi-Agent System**: Specialized agents for different development phases
- ğŸ§  **RAG Integration**: Knowledge management with local/MongoDB storage
- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Robust Error Handling**: Graceful degradation and recovery
- ğŸ“Š **Performance Monitoring**: Comprehensive metrics and optimization
- ğŸ¨ **Template System**: Pre-configured project templates
- ğŸ”„ **Hot Reload**: Development-friendly configuration
- ğŸ’° **Token Optimization**: AI cost reduction strategies

